data.name: label1.Text
data.value:
OverKart64 Designer Edition is a tool for map makers and content creators to design new courses for Mario Kart 64. It features an all-in-one geometry compiler that takes properly formatted data inputs and writes new course data directly to the ROM. It is intended to be used with the accompanying HotSwap Patch, which should be applied to your Mario Kart 64 ROM prior to using this tool.
This is the product of a contribution of knowledge gathered by multiple people.
